"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/NxoMsSBpUUVZtXFPOh6pv.png?height=1976&width=3365)\\n\\n## The problem: \\n\\nI ask myself what is a noticeable barrier to Alien Boys growth? What are the most common ‘problems’ I’ve heard since mint day?? \\n\\nThe ‘aesthetic’. People say they don’t look good.\\n\\n## Starting point: \\n\\nMuch of this comes down to preference. But not all of it. So I ask myself what of the critique do I think is fair, and I come to the background colors and some of the more aggressive-looking traits.\\n\\nSo now I ask myself where can I add value in an effort to help solve some of this?? (For future creators: this is how you align incentives)\\n\\nCan I work on the traits? No. Can I work on the backgrounds? Yes. So now we iterate.\\n\\n## Three pillars:\\n\\nWe are looking to create a couple of pillars: \\n\\n* are they dope (desirable) \\n* are they easy to swap in (frictionless) \\n* do they add value (aligned)\\n\\n## Inspiration:\\n\\nThe past couple of days I started playing around with a derivative idea from Jack Butcher’s Fudenza - a derivative of Tyler Hobbs Fidenza. \\n\\nFreedenza. Degenza. $FOCKDENZA. etc \\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/y8YL_xuR9IkqNebQHKaUo.png?height=1350&width=1080)\\n\\nIt then made sense to get an iteration in with alien boys as I now know what I’m looking for. \\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/85uSUFP4S3Hn3W5GvPNQg.jpeg?height=2000&width=2000)\\n\\nFrom here it’s trial and error until we strike gold.\",\"timestamp\":1641717470,\"title\":\"Idea Discovery: Alien Boys\"},\"digest\":\"oYU_pmnVud118HFMGH9EqKY1gaG_PUbaF_IY97orbeQ\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x869c9009A0d8279B63D83040a1aCC96a6Ad8Bf89\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"FlK71dzIMCvmS_r0WrvRAODkybek5Z0CrlfwjgRQxwI\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"UjrOsK4Qz1Mg5yrkG3gMRiyIjoxHv47VLCTJHyu6oxU\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"hwVmO9qO2TvFrL1a99LAP6Hi3KGuzHLSql6PRUa6w3E9yP9vwSzy_5QF-Q6kgnmF32C5sXD4gk5B-saeDHWtPQ\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x540f3da2be1ed4e2d8ceaadf072da42a98d6459413db361ac6977909e64ddc273550b29a750c1e651af115aa1df4b761e90c047b2920e3542af4d34b24e96abd1b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"FlK71dzIMCvmS_r0WrvRAODkybek5Z0CrlfwjgRQxwI\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"UjrOsK4Qz1Mg5yrkG3gMRiyIjoxHv47VLCTJHyu6oxU\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"oYU_pmnVud118HFMGH9EqKY1gaG_PUbaF_IY97orbeQ\"}"